Package org.rogatio.circlead.control

Class Repository

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.rogatio.circlead.control.Repository
  • public final class Repository
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class Repository is a singleton-representation of all loaded and handled data while runtime. This is the real core of the circlead-application.
